Uses of Class
org.jscsi.parser.datasegment.SettingsMap

  • Packages that use SettingsMap 
    Package Description
    org.jscsi.initiator
    This package contains all the core classes to provide an easy and usable iSCSI (RFC 3720) initiator.
    org.jscsi.initiator.connection
    This package contains all the states of a connection and all phases of the iSCSI (RFC 3720) implementation.
    org.jscsi.parser.datasegment
    This package provides all main classes which are needed to deserialize and serialize all the attached data segments of messages defined by the iSCSI Standard (RFC 3720).
